title: What Does It Really Mean To Be Woke?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO315
itunes:title: What Does It Really Mean To Be Woke?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO315
description: Are you "woke?" That's a phrase that's thrown around a lot these days. Sometimes it's used in politics to talk about people who say they really care about racism & injustice & sometimes it's used for dudes who think they've uncovered a worldwide conspiracy that nobody else knows about! But what does it really mean to be "woke," to have your eyes opened to what life is all about & what it takes to be happy & successful?
